            "type": "text",
            "text": "For production, implement comprehensive monitoring of the Kokoro inference API. Track metrics such as request rate, latency percentiles, and error counts using tools like Prometheus or Datadog. Set up alerts for anomalies, like sudden latency spikes. Scale horizontally by deploying multiple API instances behind a load balancer, and consider auto-scaling based on CPU or request volume. Regularly review logs for patterns, and ensure compliance with data privacy regulations by encrypting sensitive inputs."
